  <details class="elaris-detail-item" open>
    <summary><span>Benefits</span><span class="elaris-detail-toggle">+</span></summary>
    <ul class="elaris-detail-list">
      <li>Helps reduce hair fall over time</li>
      <li>Supports healthy hair regrowth and thickness</li>
      <li>Strengthens weak hair roots</li>
      <li>Improves overall hair density and volume</li>
      <li>Helps revive dull, thinning hair</li>
      <li>Supports a healthier scalp environment</li>
    </ul>
  </details>

  <details class="elaris-detail-item">
    <summary><span>Application</span><span class="elaris-detail-toggle">+</span></summary>
    <p class="elaris-detail-text">Apply a few sprays directly onto a clean, dry scalp. Gently massage to help absorption and leave it overnight. Use daily, morning and night, for best results.</p>
  </details>

  <details class="elaris-detail-item">
    <summary><span>Elaris Tricks</span><span class="elaris-detail-toggle">+</span></summary>
    <ul class="elaris-detail-list">
      <li>Apply on a clean scalp for better absorption</li>
      <li>Massage gently to stimulate circulation</li>
      <li>Stay consistent with daily use for visible results</li>
      <li>Use before bedtime to support overnight repair</li>
    </ul>
  </details>

  <details class="elaris-detail-item">
    <summary><span>Key Ingredients</span><span class="elaris-detail-toggle">+</span></summary>
    <ul class="elaris-detail-list elaris-detail-list--compact">
      <li>Anagain&trade; (Pisum Sativum Sprout Extract)</li>
      <li>Procapil&reg; (Biotinyl-Tripeptide-1, Apigenin, Oleanolic Acid)</li>
      <li>Rosemary Extract</li>
      <li>Acetyl Tetrapeptide-3</li>
      <li>D-Panthenol</li>
      <li>Niacinamide</li>
    </ul>
  </details>

  <div class="elaris-product-snapshot">
    <div class="elaris-snapshot-row"><span class="elaris-snapshot-label">Good for:</span><span>All hair types, especially thinning and weak hair</span></div>
    <div class="elaris-snapshot-row"><span class="elaris-snapshot-label">Feels like:</span><span>A fresh, non-greasy mist that absorbs quickly</span></div>
    <div class="elaris-snapshot-row"><span class="elaris-snapshot-label">Looks like:</span><span>Fuller, thicker-looking hair over time</span></div>
    <div class="elaris-snapshot-row"><span class="elaris-snapshot-label">Smells like:</span><span>A clean, herbal-fresh scent</span></div>
    <p class="elaris-product-fyi">Non-Sticky &middot; Fast Absorbing &middot; No Greasy Residue &middot; Daily Use</p>
