    <summary><span>What's inside</span><span class="elaris-detail-toggle">+</span></summary>
    <div class="elaris-detail-body">
      <p class="elaris-detail-text">A fast-absorbing scalp spray designed to strengthen roots, reduce hair fall, and support healthy hair regrowth for thicker, fuller-looking hair over time.</p>
      <div class="elaris-ingredient-highlight">
        <h4>Anagain&trade;</h4>
        <p>Helps revitalize hair follicles and promote new hair growth</p>
      </div>
      <div class="elaris-ingredient-highlight">
        <h4>Procapil&reg;</h4>
        <p>Strengthens hair roots and reduces thinning for a denser scalp</p>
      </div>
      <p class="elaris-detail-note">Also made with Rosemary Extract, Acetyl Tetrapeptide-3, D-Panthenol, and Niacinamide.</p>
    </div>
  </details>

  <div class="elaris-spread-tags">
    <p class="elaris-spread-tags__label">Spread it on for:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>hair fall control</li>
      <li>stronger roots</li>
      <li>thicker-looking hair</li>
    </ul>
